entries.title: 2 freshmen revive Wisconsin Legislature’s socialist caucus
entries.description: MADISON, Wis. (AP) — It’s been 90 years, but socialism is back in the Wisconsin Legislature.

entries.title: Poll: Michiganders approve of right to work by 2:1 ratio
entries.description: (The Center Square) – Approximately twice as many Michiganders approve of a right-to-work law than oppose it, according to a statewide poll released Thursday by TargetPoint Consulting on behalf of the Mackinac Center for Public Policy.
